Titolo: Massive Assault Network 2

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Massive Assault Network 2 is a massively multiplayer online game published by Wargaming.  The game is a turn-based futuristic military simulation.  The game is science fiction and takes place in the future, with the Free States Union vying for power against the Phantom League.  Opponents square off against each other on a particular planet and fight to control all of its nations.  Each player is given secret ally nations, and each nation has a limited amount of resources for building units.  The game comes in both a free and subscription version.  The free version provides full unit set and one level, where the subscription version provides access to several levels.



Genere: Turn-based tactics

Valutazione: N/A
